#{{countable}} Someone who [[sleep]]s.
#{{countable}} A [[saboteur]] or [[terrorist]] who lives [[unobtrusively]] in a [[community]] until [[activated]] by a [[prearranged]] [[signal]]; may be part of a [[sleeper cell]].
#{{countable}} A [[railroad]] [[sleeping car]].
#{{countable}} A [[horizontal]] [[wooden]] or [[concrete]] [[structural]] [[member]] that [[support]]s and [[tie]]s together [[railway]] [[line]]s.
# Something that [[achieve]]s [[unexpected]] [[success]] after an [[interval]] of time.

